(11489, 'Tolexine 100mg 10 cap', 'تولكسين 100مجم 10 كبسولات', '', '19', 'Doxycycline', 'Al hikma pharmaceuticals', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', 'مضاد حيوي.', 'Antibiotic', '100mg', 'Doxycycline is indicated for the treatment of various infections by gram-positive and gram-negative bacteria, aerobes and anaerobes, as well other types of bacteria, including:
